Narro is a web application that allows online translation and coordination.
    
You can ask for help in the google group available via email or via web here:
    http://groups.google.com/group/narro-project

You can follow the project progress via its blog here:
    http://narro-project.blogspot.com/
    
Narro is open source and licensed GPLv2. You can browse the project code here:
    http://code.google.com/p/narro
    